values: And here I thought I would have to undergoing mayor repairs after yesterday. Apparently, the City is interested in causing trauma to the residents. I'm not sure if that's amusing or not, I feel somewhat apathetic toward the whole mess, even after having my arm ripped off only to have it in tact several hours later. Perhaps it's because I'm not human, or even of flesh. I would imagine flesh-types are having a shaky morning after a day like yesterday. However... This snow I could become quite contented with. I'm going to play with it - it's my element after all. [ooc; Fisheh is the general of ice so she's a happy Fisheh today because of the snow. She'll be off by the Drowning Pool engaging in a bit of icicle target practice ]

Hn. Sunlight or not, makes no difference to me.

What strange customs humans had... Still, it's pretty interesting to over-see.

...'ch! Little things seem to be bugging me more than they would do normally.

I'm going to be staying at the lab today and there had better be damn good reasons for bothering me if any of you stop by. <font size=1>X is the only exception to that.</font>

<font size=1>[ Walking down the street toward the fountain area, pausing then and inclining her hips to one side as she taps into a particular frequency ]</font>

X? I'm near the fountain. Are you still in the vicinity?

Saya, your payment has been delivered as par agreement. Thank you for your hard work, It was lovely~ doing business with you! ♥ I... made vocal contact with X. Not the Copy, either... X the original form. This city does have an interesting way of shuffling things around... I'm a little overwhelmed, honestly... I hope we get to speak again soon. There is... so much I want to ask, but I can't think what at the same time.
...I'm just not going there. Here's hoping not everyone has gone mad.

[ Private from Asuka ] We need a HUGE ribbon that can be tied around at least part of an Eva... And find or make a BIG 'Happy Birthday' sign by the 14th of this month. C'mon~ one of you must have something like that hidden under your bed or something. [ /Private ] [ Private to anyone working on the reactivation of Unit 02 ] If we progress as we are, I'm quite confident we can get Unit 02 operational by the 14th. Agreed? It'd be a nice gift for the little girlie, hmm? [ /Private ]

I do not regret. Not a damned thing.




<font size=1>[ooc; She may be lying... chances are, she'd never say though :P]</font>
...I believe I have discovered that the alternation of gender has left me quite apathetic to the concept. I don't see what all the fuss is about.

...'ch! To degrade myself to part-take in trivial labour or not... It's not like I need employment or anything, but I suppose if anyone wants to hire an ex-general as a mercenary or hacker we can come to some agreement of sorts.

With all the panic flying around and the explosions it's seems almost cruel of me to simply find "The Drowning Pool" area a calm position from which to observe the unfolding events. After all, fire reflected on water is such a rare but beautiful sight, and stray fire surviving on water always amused me. What would fire expect to achieve on the water, I wonder. I believe I may have found myself a place of temporary contentment.

Objects falling from the sky and... C... cats...? W-what the hell is this?! Does this happen regularly? [ooc; Fisheh-reploid doesn't like the falling kitties D: She wouldn't admit she's freaked out by them though, of course :P ]

All my communications are down.

I can't contact anyone <strike>not that I want to or was planning to right now anyway... Jerks.</strike>

Ugh! This is so frustrating, not to mention humiliating. How is it I, Leviathan, Ice General under Master X can't even hack into this ancient network? It's so backwards, I'll need more time to adjust my readings to this place.

<strike><font size=1>I want to go home.</strike></font>
